### ============================================================
### API de Adoção de Pets - Testes REST Client
### Instale a extensão "REST Client" no VS Code para usar este arquivo
### ============================================================

### Variáveis de ambiente
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@adminToken = COLE_O_TOKEN_ADMIN_AQUI
@adopterToken = COLE_O_TOKEN_ADOPTER_AQUI

### ============================================================
### HEALTH CHECK
### ============================================================

### Verificar API online
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### ============================================================
### AUTENTICAÇÃO
### ============================================================

### [POST] Login como admin (use o token retornado nas variáveis acima)
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@pets.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### [POST] Login como adopter
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

###

### [POST] Login com credenciais inválidas (deve retornar 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@pets.com",
  "password": "senhaerrada"
}

### ============================================================
### USUÁRIOS - Rotas Públicas
### ============================================================

### [POST] Cadastrar novo usuário adopter (público)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "senha123",
  "phone": "51999999999",
  "role": "adopter"
}

###

### [POST] Cadastro público ignora role enviada e cria adopter
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Silva",
  "email": "maria@email.com",
  "password": "senha123",
  "phone": "51888888888",
  "role": "admin"
}

###

### [POST] Tentar cadastrar email duplicado (deve retornar 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Outro Usuário",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### ============================================================
### USUÁRIOS - Rotas Protegidas (Admin)
### ============================================================

### [GET] Listar todos os usuários (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### [GET] Buscar usuário por ID (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### [PUT] Atualizar usuário (admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva Atualizado",
  "phone": "51777777777"
}

###

### [DELETE] Remover usuário (admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/3
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### [GET] Tentar listar usuários sem token (deve retornar 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

###

### [GET] Adotante buscando próprio perfil (adopter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adopterToken}}

###

### [GET] Adotante tentando ver outro usuário (deve retornar 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adopterToken}}

### ============================================================
### PETS - Rota Pública
### ============================================================

### [GET] Listar pets disponíveis (público - sem token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/pets/available

### ============================================================
### PETS - Rotas Protegidas (Admin)
### ============================================================

### [GET] Listar todos os pets (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### [POST] Cadastrar novo pet (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rex",
  "age": 3,
  "species": "dog",
  "size": "medium",
  "description": "Cão amigável e brincalhão, vacinado e castrado"
}

###

### [POST] Cadastrar outro pet (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mimi",
  "age": 2,
  "species": "cat",
  "size": "small",
  "description": "Gatinha dócil e carinhosa"
}

###

### [GET] Buscar pet por ID (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/pets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### [PUT] Atualizar pet (admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/pets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rex Atualizado",
  "age": 4,
  "description": "Cão adulto muito dócil"
}

###

### [DELETE] Remover pet disponível (admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/pets/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### [POST] Tentar cadastrar pet sem campos obrigatórios (deve retornar 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pet Incompleto"
}

###

### [POST] Tentar cadastrar pet com porte inválido (deve retornar 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pet Inválido",
  "species": "dog",
  "size": "gigante"
}

###

### [POST] Adotante tentando cadastrar pet (deve retornar 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{adopterToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pet Não Autorizado",
  "species": "dog",
  "size": "small"
}

### ============================================================
### ADOÇÕES
### ============================================================

### [POST] Realizar adoção de pet (adopter)
POST {{baseUrl}}/adoptions
Authorization: Bearer {{adopterToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pet_id": 1
}

###

### [POST] Tentar adotar o mesmo pet novamente (deve retornar 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/adoptions
Authorization: Bearer {{adopterToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pet_id": 1
}

###

### [GET] Listar todas as adoções (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/adoptions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### [POST] Admin tentando adotar um pet (deve retornar 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/adoptions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pet_id": 1
}

###

### [DELETE] Tentar remover pet já adotado (deve retornar 400)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/pets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
